com.cloudofficeprint

Interface IResponse

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Response, ResponsePolling

    public interface IResponse
    Interface for dealing with the Cloud Office Print server's response to a printjob request.

      • downloadLocally

        void downloadLocally(java.lang.String path)
              throws java.io.IOException
        Downloads the file locally to the given path, filename needs to be specified at the end of the path, not the extension. Creates the file at given path if it doesn't exist yet, overwrites it otherwise.
        Parameters:
        path - local path ending
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - If the file is not found.

        Contains value of the HTTP response header named "Template-Hash" given by the Cloud Office Print server.
        Returns:
        hash of the template of the print job.
